name: EAT.ch
tag_list: order-food-online, essen-online-bestellen, pizzakurier, delivery-restaurant, take-out, takeaway
overview:
EAT.ch allows it’s user to order food online from a growing base of delivery restaurants in Switzerland.

As an intermediary platform EAT.ch on one hand provides to the user a convenient and fast way to order food online from a big variety of delivery restaurants and on the other hand the restaurants owners are helped to improve their business by generating more revenues and providing a better service quality to its customers.

Today EAT.ch is the leading Swiss player and part of the Just-Eat group, which is the worldwide leader in its sector with more than 20 000 restaurants in their network on four continents. Among the Just-Eat investors are Index Ventures, Greylock Partners and Redpoint Ventures.
